// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0151 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 8bea6e59-528e-55e0-a4b0-56d12776a6da

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
